---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="Who I am and what I write about here."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-07-07')}
	aiUsage="assisted"
>
	<p>I'm Asif.</p>

	<p>
		i've been building software for 15+ years. Frontend, backend, emails, infra,
		data, mobile. all of it, basically. Still a backend engineer at heart tho.
	</p>

	<p>
		Right now i build AI software at a venture firm. CRM, agents, internal tools,
		and a LOT of plumbing. I'm the only engineer here, so the job is part
		building, part fixing, part writing things down before i forget why something
		works.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog is the overflow. Shipping notes, mistakes that became rules,
		open-weight model stuff i'm following too closely, and sometimes family.
	</p>

	<p>Dad of three, so that usually wins the calendar.</p>

	<p>
		Four humors: mostly fire, some earth. Choleric with a melancholic streak
		(annoyingly fair).
	</p>
</Layout>
